---
description: Restart the dev server after most code changes
alwaysApply: true
---

Restart the dev server yourself in the background after finishing work, unless the change is clearly non-breaking and trivial (e.g. simple CSS-only tweaks, copy, or other minor `src/**` edits that HMR handles cleanly).

When restarting: `lsof -ti:3001 | xargs kill -9 2>/dev/null; sleep 1; NO_OPEN=1 npm run dev`

Default to restarting for anything that touches `server/**`, `shared/**`, config, dependencies, game logic, sockets, types used by the server, or when unsure.
